Remote Purple is a client/server-combo for using Pidgin remotely.
Server is available at https://github.com/ninnnu/Remote-Purple

Remote Purple for Harmattan is client for N9(50).

== Features ==
Supported:
* Show buddylist
* Show conversations and their messages
* Send/receive new messages.

Closing conversations isn't supported (yet).

== Screenshots ==
Buddylist: http://ninnnu.kuism.at/rpqt-blist.png
Conversation: http://ninnnu.kuism.at/mobile-rp-conv.png

== Requirements ==
* Maemo Harmattan / MeeGo-device. ATM desktop Qt probably works, too, since Qt Mobility isn't really used.
* Google Protobuf-library.
